com.rapidminer.extension.indatabase

Class OperatorMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.rapidminer.extension.indatabase.OperatorMap

  • public class OperatorMap
extends java.lang.Object
    OperatorMap defines the In-database equivalents of the standard RapidMiner operators and provides methods to query these equivalents and decide if a conversion is doable.
